# Commit, push, deploy

For this repository, after completing each user-requested change:

1. Commit only files related to the change (exclude unrelated drift such as `package-lock.json` unless intentionally updated).
2. Push to `origin/master`.
3. Confirm the GitHub Pages deploy workflow succeeds.

Live site: **https://savethedate.neophitou.com**

Do not skip commit/push/deploy unless the user explicitly asks to hold changes locally.
